msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_company_team
msgid ""
"Iris is responsible for creating cost-effective travel packages, ensuring "
"clients can enjoy their adventures without compromising on quality."
msgstr ""
"Iris is verantwoordelijk voor het samenstellen van kosteneffectieve "
"reispakketten, zodat klanten van hun avonturen kunnen genieten zonder in te "
"leveren op kwaliteit."

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"It would take too long to describe day by day the sights, sounds, and people "
"that we came across. Ireland was fantastic."
msgstr ""
"Het zou te lang duren om van dag tot dag de bezienswaardigheden, geluiden en "
"mensen die we tegenkwamen te beschrijven. Ierland was fantastisch."

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_masonry_block_default_template
msgid "Italy"
msgstr "Italië"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_image_text
msgid "Itinerary Planning"
msgstr "Planning van je route"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_quotes_carousel
msgid "Jacques and Marie"
msgstr "Jacques en Marie"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_banner
msgid "Let's <br/>travel the world"
msgstr "Laten we <br/>de wereld rondreizen"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_quotes_carousel
msgid "Linda and Paulo"
msgstr "Linda en Paulo"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_company_team
msgid "Meet our travel agents"
msgstr "Maak kennis met onze reisagenten"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_company_team
msgid ""
"Mich ensures the smooth execution of all travel plans, leveraging his "
"industry expertise to guarantee a seamless client experience."
msgstr ""
"Mich zorgt voor een soepele uitvoering van alle reisplannen en maakt gebruik "
"van zijn kennis van de sector om een naadloze klantervaring te garanderen."

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_picture
msgid "Old Harry Rocks, Isle of Purbeck"
msgstr "Oude Harry Rotsen, Eiland Purbeck"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_text_image
msgid ""
"Our team travels widely the globe to bring our clients first-hand knowledge "
"of upcoming destinations, new \"hot\" hotels and ships, local restaurants, "
"neighborhood hangouts, bars, pubs, the best. beaches and places to visit and "
"not to see."
msgstr ""
"Ons team reist de hele wereld over om onze klanten uit de eerste hand kennis "
"te geven over nieuwe bestemmingen, nieuwe gewilde hotels en schepen, lokale "
"restaurants, uitgangsplekken in de buurt, bars, pubs, de beste stranden en "
"plaatsen om al dan niet te bezoeken."

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_image_text
msgid ""
"Our vision is to make travel planning stress free and make travel more fun. "
"No matter the type of trip you have in mind, we have the resources and "
"expertise necessary to create the perfect trip"
msgstr ""
"Onze visie is om de organisatie stressvrij en het reizen leuker te maken. "
"Ongeacht het soort reis dat je in gedachten hebt, hebben wij de middelen en "
"de expertise die nodig zijn om de perfecte reis te creëren"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_showcase
msgid "Personalized Itineraries"
msgstr "Persoonlijke routes"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_masonry_block_default_template
msgid "Romania"
msgstr "Roemenië"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_quotes_carousel
msgid "Rose and Peter"
msgstr "Roos en Peter"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_showcase
msgid "Seamless Travel Experience"
msgstr "Naadloze reiservaring"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_picture
msgid ""
"Set off on an unforgettable adventure to the world's most breathtaking "
"locations, thoughtfully curated just for you."
msgstr ""
"Vertrek op een onvergetelijk avontuur naar de meest adembenemende locaties "
"ter wereld, speciaal voor jou samengesteld."

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"The parts of the country we visited were beautiful, people were friendly, "
"everything we ate was delicious, and there were many fun things to see and "
"do."
msgstr ""
"De delen van het land die we bezochten waren prachtig, de mensen waren "
"vriendelijk, alles wat we aten was heerlijk en er waren veel leuke dingen te "
"zien en te doen."

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_aviato.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Thematools"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_company_team
msgid ""
"Tony is dedicated to crafting personalized travel experiences, ensuring "
"every client's journey is tailored to their unique preferences."
msgstr ""
"Tony is toegewijd aan het creëren van persoonlijke reiservaringen en zorgt "
"ervoor dat de reis van elke klant is afgestemd op hun unieke voorkeuren."

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_title
msgid "Top Destinations"
msgstr "Beste bestemmingen"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_showcase
msgid ""
"We select only the best destinations, ensuring your travel experience is "
"nothing short of extraordinary."
msgstr ""
"We selecteren alleen de beste bestemmingen, zodat je reiservaring niets "
"minder dan buitengewoon is."

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_text_image
msgid "What we can do, <b>for you</b>"
msgstr "Wat de <b>voor jou</b> kunnen doen"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_showcase
msgid "Why Choose Us"
msgstr "Waarom voor ons kiezen"

#. module: theme_aviato
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_aviato.s_showcase
msgid ""
"Your journey is tailored to match your preferences, making every trip "
"uniquely yours."
msgstr ""
"Je reis wordt afgestemd op je voorkeuren, waardoor elke reis uniek voor jou "
"is."
